title: Agrilus suvorovi
description:
Agrilus suvorovi found dead within the larval galleries on Populus tremula
Grand Carti, Feschaux, Belgium, 07.VII.2021
Body length : 8 mm

- Top : Ventral view of the right middle femur
- Middle : Dorsal view of the left middle femur
- Botom : Detail of the posterior tarsa

- Focus stack of 14-31  images
- Microscope objective (Nikon M Plan 10x 160/0.25)
- Olympus OM-D E-M1 Mark II
- High res mode
label: Original
